            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯昌(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2431:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2431\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2431-TW</a>)29日10:41下跌1.65元，股價跌停報15.2元，委買3張、委賣4張，成交4,383張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為電源供應器。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯昌(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2431:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2431\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2431-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲31.64%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.98%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+807 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+785 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+22 張</li> <li>融資增減：-127 張</li> <li>融券增減：+50 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
